==English==

===Adjective===
'''selfless'''
# Having, exhibiting or motivated by no concern for oneself; [[unselfish]].
#: ''In a '''selfless''' act of gratitude for saving his mother's life, Peter committed to giving money to his local [[breat cancer]] charity each year for the rest of his life.''

